{"tid":684607,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人眼嘅象素係幾多?","createTime":"2018-05-30T16:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T18:15:27.000Z","uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8706d54dd3f14f10dad887ebe711664735ee3d0","tid":684607,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"576 megapixels<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/futurism.com/what-is-the-resolution-of-the-human-eye/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Ffuturism.com%2Fwhat-is-the-resolution-of-the-human-eye%2Famp%2F&d=A9geYZzDo9425E11XSqJYEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=9882b468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/futurism.com/what-is-the-resolution-of-the-human-eye/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n但應該因人而異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  實有啲人對眼好啲<br />\n軍人會唔會練到好高象素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFPS又係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人有興趣傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa354a5453440e9def05bee7c4fbb8a5e88b93f6","tid":684607,"uid":21423,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4886abd5894fa5b12d4bdb9d4df7441119c9e4ea","tid":684607,"uid":137768,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fa354a5453440e9def05bee7c4fbb8a5e88b93f6","tid":684607,"uid":21423,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n像素 像素 像素"},{"pid":"f7597a5c50ac81bb94cd6a38793459fc5c6a396e","tid":684607,"uid":89064,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問下隻象囉</blockquote><br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"f76994881121bd625d677b35e0e63e75947c774f","tid":684607,"uid":2474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4886abd5894fa5b12d4bdb9d4df7441119c9e4ea","tid":684607,"uid":137768,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fa354a5453440e9def05bee7c4fbb8a5e88b93f6","tid":684607,"uid":21423,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n像素 像素 像素"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:15:27.000Z","msg":"The eye is not a single frame snapshot camera. It is more like a video stream.<br />\nConsider a view in front of you that is 90 degrees by 90 degrees, like looking through an open window at a scene. The number of pixels would be,<br />\n90 degrees * 60 arc-minutes/degree * 1/0.3 * 90 * 60 * 1/0.3 = 324,000,000 pixels (324 megapixels).<br />\nBut practically if including peripheral vision, that's 120*<br />\n120 * 120 * 60 * 60 / (0.3 * 0.3) = 576 megapixels.<br />\n120* is just a measure i took for peripheral vision which is more certain but in reality a blur vision extend to 180*, that will give more pixels but this won't only include the single capture by eye but also the memory of the vision in previous stance.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/What-is-the-pixel-clarity-of-an-average-human-eye\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2FWhat-is-the-pixel-clarity-of-an-average-human-eye&d=A9geYZzDo9425E11XSqJYEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=285a1d5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.quora.com/What-is-the-pixel-clarity-of-an-average-human-eye</a>"}]}